name: Slash the Nightmare - Brook Draws His Freezing Sword!
summary: In the dense mist, Brook is surprised to see his old friends, the Rumbar Pirates and Laboon. They reminisce about the old days and play music together, however, they suddenly attack Brook.

show.name: One Piece
show.summary: One Piece animation is based on the successful comic by Eiichiro Oda. The comic has sold more than 260 million copies. The success doesn't stop; the One Piece animation series is in its top 5 TV ratings for kids programs in Japan for past few years and the series' most recent feature film title "One Piece Film Z" which was released on December 2012 has gathered 5.6 million viewers so far. The success goes beyond borders; receives high popularity on animation at terrestrial channel in Taiwan, no.1 rating on animation at a DTT channel in France, received high popularity among age 3-13 on a terrestrial channel in Germany in year 2010. The animation series has been broadcasted in many parts of the world: USA, UK, Australia, France, Spain, Portugal, Germany, Italy, Greece, Turkey, Israel, South Korea, Taiwan, China, Hong Kong, Philippine, Thailand, Singapore, Malaysia, Indonesia, Ecuador, Nicaragua, Chile, Mexico, Brazil, and etc.

show.name: Battle Through the Heavens
show.summary: In a land where no magic is present. A land where the strong make the rules and weak have to obey. A land filled with alluring treasures and beauty, yet also filled with unforeseen danger. Three years ago, Xiao Yan, who had shown talents none had seen in decades, suddenly lost everything. His powers, his reputation, and his promise to his mother. What sorcery has caused him to lose all of his powers? And why has his fiancee suddenly shown up?

show.name: Wu Shen Zhu Zai
show.summary:
The protagonist Qin Chen, who was originally the top genius in the military domain, was conspired by the people to fall into the death canyon in the forbidden land of the mainland. Qin Chen, who was inevitably dead, unexpectedly triggered the power of the mysterious ancient sword.

Three hundred years later, in a remote part of the Tianwu mainland, a boy of the same name accidentally inherited Qin Chen's will. As the beloved grandson of King Dingwu of the Daqi National Army, due to the birth father's birth, the mother and son were treated coldly in Dingwu's palace and lived together. In order to rewrite the myth of the strong man in hope of the sun, and to protect everything he loves, Qin Chen resolutely took up the responsibility of maintaining the five kingdoms of the world and set foot on the road of martial arts again.

show.name: I Annoyed Millions of Cultivators
show.summary: I Annoyed Millions of Cultivators tells the story of a Jiangbei student who fought valiantly at the subway station and was blessed by the system. Fortunately, he hosts the system and travels to another world. In this different world full of cultivators, Jiangbei had turned from a trash in a small town to a child genius in everyone's eyes. Relying on the system, Jiangbei has started the road of improvement and become stronger just by playing System, and irritating people. After a series of chaos and poetry battles, Jiangbei gradually developed feelings for his relatives here.

show.name: Supreme Galaxy
show.summary: The Star Sect was once the most dazzling clan of the Blue Earth Star, the Star Clan, accidentally obtained the "Star Map", which attracted the prying eyes of the Lord of the Universe , who, in order to obtain the Star Map, induced the senior members of the Star Clan to go to the Sacred Star Domain and imprisoned them in the "Sacred Star Domain". Only one guardian elder Zhuge Haohan and young master Chu Xinghe and a few young disciples remained in the Star Sect. They were suppressed by other sects due to lack of strength, and were taken away by the Ying Clan . In order to regain its glory, the young master Chu Xinghe led his disciples to break through twelve star realms and defeat the 12 Star Practitioners under the Lord of the Universe . In the end, he saved his father and all the people of the Star Sect.

show.name: DDT Pro Wrestling
show.summary: DDT Pro-Wrestling (DDTプロレスリング DDT Puroresuringu) is a Japanese professional wrestling promotion based in Shinjuku, Tokyo, Japan. Its name stands for Dramatic Dream Team, which was the promotion's official name from 1997 to 2004. Founded in March 1997 by Shintaro Muto, but the promotion was eventually bought and managed by Shoichi Ichimiya until December 2005, when Sanshiro Takagi took over as the new president. DDT became one of the top promotions in Japanese indie wrestling by creating a unique sports entertainment style, often parodying WWE, with a Japanese puroresu flair to the matches.

show.name: Xian Wang de Ri Chang Sheng Huo
show.summary: As a cultivation genius who has achieved a new realm every two years since he was a year old, Wang Ling is a near-invincible existence with prowess far beyond his control. But now that he's sixteen, he faces his greatest battle yet – Senior High School. With one challenge after another popping up, his plans for a low-key high school life seem further and further away…

show.name: Warm Meet You
show.summary: Zhao Nuan Nuan is a comic book artist with outstanding drawing skills who has always dreamed of becoming the best in China, but has repeatedly failed. Hopeless, she is forced to go on a blind date, but mistakes a passing Gu Yi Chen whom she was supposed to meet on a blind date. Zhao Nuan Nuan's only drawback is that she is very unlucky, but ironically, she accidentally discovers that while she is getting closer to Gu And Chen, her luck is changing for the better. In order to change her twenty years of bad luck, Nuan Nuan did not hesitate to disguise herself as a man to apply for a permanent job as a cleaner in CEO Gu Yi Chen's office to get her luck, not knowing that Gu Yi Chen suffers from an unprecedented "allergy to touching the opposite sex".

show.name: Betrayed Love
show.summary:
The story of three women who are crazy about love, and three men who are trapped in love.
Guan Xin, the heiress of Guan Group and is respected by all directors. Her husband Shen Zhuo works for Guan Group and reports to her. And she is also gentle and attentive at home. The most important thing is that she also has a good friend-Xu Jing, with whom you can talk about everything.
Reporter Ding Myung Ran considers her job her life, and in order to find the truth, she does not hesitate to take risks in many investigations. She knows many financial sharks and celebrities, and can also smell a sensation in advance.
Guan Xin finds out that her husband is cheating on her with her best friend and at a birthday party, decides to talk to him. Ding Meng Ran felt that something was wrong with Shen Zhuo, and later witnessed how Shen Zhuo pushed Guan Xin off a cliff.

show.name: Women Walk the Line
show.summary: A pair of post-90s besties have chosen very different paths in life. Upon graduation, one stayed in Shanghai to focus on her career while the other returned to their hometown to get married. In recent years, they encounter unprecedented difficulties. For many years, Yuan Ge has been married to her job and hasn't bothered investing in relationships. As her health takes a hit, she starts to make changes in her life. For eight years, Gu Qiao has made constant concessions for her husband only to be given divorce papers in the end. This time around, she's determined to restart her career. While both ladies have completely different personalities, they are equally tough and brave. In a metropolis full of opportunities, it is easy to lose your away. Not afraid of falling, they are persistent and join hands in overcoming difficulties to complete the transformation of youth and usher in a new chapter in their thirties.

show.name: Peerless Martial Spirit
show.summary: On the continent of the Dragon Vein, the weak were like the ants. Anyone who wanted to become a powerhouse could only make it through cultivation. Only the strong could fly into heaven, drill into the earth, move the mountains and overturn the sea. And the one who reached the king's realm could even shake heaven and earth… A young man called Chen Feng, due to the severe damage of his pubic region, could never cultivate for his whole life. But some day he inherited a drop of blood from his mysterious master and obtained a transcendental physique for cultivation, then opened a new chapter of his legendary life… (novelupdate)

name: Adventslys
summary: It is the second Sunday in Advent, and candles are lit. But they must also be extinguished! This presents major challenges for the remaining participants.

show.name: 24-stjerners julekalender
show.summary: Markus has gathered 24 celebrities to compete in the Christmas strip's biggest challenges. Who is left as this year's Christmas star? Norwegian reality Christmas calendar.

show.name: Xing Yuan Zhi Zhu
show.summary: Su Jiu, a useless young man, was hit by the divine stone "Xingyuan", from an ordinary student without any training qualifications, to become the new master of Xingyuan. The two super beauties of Wanjie, You Yihan and Shen Mengxue, also came to pursue "Xingyuan". The two of them borrowed strongly in the name of avoiding the enemy's family. In order to attract Su Jiu to enter their own sect, they temporarily reached an agreement to teach them together. Su Jiu practiced. Unexpectedly, Su Jiuxiu, who has "Xingyuan", has made rapid progress, far beyond the imagination of the two girls.

show.name: New Japan Pro Wrestling
show.summary: New Japan Pro Wrestling (NJPW) is the largest professional wrestling promotion in Japan and the second largest promotion in the world.

summary: A Songbayanan of "Maalaala Mo Kaya" letter senders banks on their knowledge of songs as they take on a series of five tricky sing-along challenges in hopes of winning the coveted jackpot prize.

show.name: Everybody, Sing!
show.summary: Everybody, Sing! is a musical game show featuring a community as contestants singing together for a jackpot prize of more than ₱2,000,000 which will be equally split among themselves.

name: Calles siste stunt
summary: Calle's crazy world editors have to make the final feature for season 9, but Calle has disappeared without a trace.

show.name: Calles gale verden
show.summary: Calle's Crazy World documents the life of Calle Hellevang-Larsen, "Norway's most hidden cameraman", the country's lauded and crowned king of the TV art of hidden camera. He is at the top of the pyramid and lives a life of hustle and bustle, surrounded by parties and glamour, loose friends and his faithful French-speaking best friend. But there is a cost to keeping the place on the throne, and in order to preserve the people's hunger for hidden cameras, it is important to constantly come up with new and ground-breaking ideas.

name: Espiral, 87. Cara B
summary: Sento witnesses Marc and Lucas' car accident and, to protect his friend, decides to lie and assure the police that Lucas was driving. Marc, however, feels guilty and hesitates to confess while Nuria discovers that there are more people who know the truth and are willing to denounce him.

show.name: La Ruta
show.summary: La Ruta is the journey of a group of friends from El Perelló, from their farewell in a crowded Ruta Destroy, in 1993, until the day they entered Barraca for the first time, in 1981, when both they and "the party" they still preserved their innocence. La Ruta recounts the more than ten years that Valencia spent dancing, a few years that we would all like to live and that only a few can remember.

name: The Badge of Power
summary: Adam's official 2IC badge finally arrives, but when Beeanca convinces Sarah to try it on they witness the true dark powers that lie within... Maybe.

show.name: Rostered On
show.summary: Shaun hasn't quite figured out what he wants to do in life. Instead, he has found himself on the wrong side of 30, working in a job he hates, dealing with painful customers, cliché co-workers, and taking orders from the ignorant.

show.name: World Wonder Ring STARDOM
show.summary: World Wonder Ring Stardom, legal name Kabushiki Gaisha Stardom (株式会社スターダム Kabushiki Gaisha Sutādamu) and often referred to simply as Stardom (stylized as STARD✪M),[2] is a Japanese joshi puroresu or women's professional wrestling promotion, founded in September 2010 by former Hyper Visual Fighting Arsion and JDStar promoter Rossy Ogawa, retired wrestler, model and mixed martial artist Fuka Kakimoto and veteran professional wrestler Nanae Takahashi. Stardom quickly became one of the top joshi puroresu promotions, largely thanks to gravure idol Yuzuki Aikawa becoming the promotion's public face.

name: 41-Я НЕДЕЛЯ: «Редакция.News»
summary: "The Tree of invincibility", swamps on the front line, Piggy and Stepashka at the front, a scandal in an Irish pub, parcels with explosives, gaslighting of the year, sale of "Crosses".

show.name: Редакция
show.summary: The author's journalistic program of Alexey Pivovarov, where he asks questions and interviews guests, makes reports on actual themes, as well as on entertaining topics.

name: Ding Dong Merrily on High
summary: Sigrid and Pørni visit Anne's grave, and Pørni learns something important about Bjørnar's baby. She meets an old client with an agenda, and on Christmas Eve Aunt Elisabeth Pørni is the only guest.

show.name: Pørni
show.summary: Pørni always puts her near and dear ones first and raises her two daughters and nephew alone. At the same time, she has to take care of her crisis-stricken father - but when does she get time for herself?

name: Årets verste dag
summary: Pørni tries to help a friend's family in trouble, and on New Year's Eve she finds herself having to solve some challenges in a not-so-Gandhi-like way.

Since the beginning of the fifth season, three hosts have shared the main wheel: Andrius Tapinas, Ignas Grinevičius, and Irma Bogdanovičiūtė.

show.name: ебаут
show.summary: "ebaut" is a frank show on vital but taboo topics.

show.name: Elvira
show.summary: Elvira works as a receptionist at a brothel run by her childhood friend, the policeman Køster. When a sex worker disappears, Elvira begins to investigate the case, which has dramatic consequences.

name: Visitation Place
summary: At the Tulsa Arena, Dwight and company test out their new plan, until a roadblock forces them to adjust and defend their turf. Tyson and his father argue about his future. Dwight gets an unexpected call.

show.name: Tulsa King
show.summary: Tulsa King follows New York mafia capo Dwight "The General" Manfredi, just after he is released from prison after 25 years and unceremoniously exiled by his boss to set up shop in Tulsa, Oklahoma. Realizing that his mob family may not have his best interests in mind, Dwight slowly builds a "crew" from a group of unlikely characters, to help him establish a new criminal empire in a place that, to him, might as well be another planet.

name: Клим Жуков о фильме «Семь самураев» (1954)
summary: Клим Жуков и Кристина Егорова разбирают фильм Дика Лоури «Семь самураев» (1954). Крестьяне бедной деревушки зависят от милости бандитов, которые нападают на них, чтобы грабить и насиловать. Крестьяне принимают решение сразиться с ними и нанимают странствующего самурая, чтобы он спас их. Крестьяне в состоянии заплатить немного, лишь чашку риса. Самурай Комбей из сострадания берется за эту работу. Он находит еще пятерых странников, готовых сражаться за еду или ради забавы. Жители деревни сначала с недоверием относятся к самураям, но со временем между ними возникают дружеские отношения. Смельчаки оказывают достойное сопротивление бандитам и прогоняют их.

show.name: Деконструкция
show.summary: An educational online project of the Prodvizhenie TV channel and the Kino-Teatr.Ru website about how the past is depicted in real cinema and what place a work of art occupied in the context of its time. From classics to modern cinema, from epic films to TV series. The experts of "Deconstruction" - historians, reenactors, writers and journalists - will take each film apart and leave no stone unturned to find historical truth and fiction

show.name: Qing Chuan Daily Life
show.summary: Because of a marriage selection, girls from all over the world gather in Xin Chuan. Yin Zheng, one of the six young masters of Xin Chuan, who keeps a low profile, and Li Wei, who just wants to work hard and not get selected, live comfortably in this hometown. They unexpectedly form a relationship, and together, start a new life where they encounter numerous situations and complement each other in overcoming them. As Yin Zheng sets up a government office and goes to court, the two gradually develop similar tastes as their hearts become in sync. They share three meals and four seasons together, and grow up with other brothers and sisters with different personalities and fates, living a warm, daily life as a Xin Chuan family together.

show.name: BMC Way: Thai Rap Mission
show.summary: Thai-Japanese hip-hop group Baby Mic Candy travels from Fukuoka to Thailand where they'll learn about the culture and search for a new member among Thai rappers. They aim to find inspiration for Thai music and earn their place at Big Mountain Music Festival 2022.

name: Thunderstorms In The Forecast
summary: Meech can't escape his old habits as he tries to stay a free man and keep BMF alive. Little does he know that his remaining crew aren't as loyal as they may seem.

show.name: The BMF Documentary: Blowing Money Fast
show.summary: The BMF Documentary: Blowing Money Fast chronicles the notorious drug syndicate, the Black Mafia Family. The series will feature exclusive audio excerpts from founding member, Demetrius Flenory, in addition to interviews with members of his family, former BMF members and celebrity insiders including Curtis "50 Cent" Jackson, T.I., 2 Chainz, and White Boy Rick.

show.name: Idol in My Living Room
show.summary: A youth melodrama that unfolds when Joy, an excellent student at Sejong Institute, and Yeo-won, a Hallyu Wave idol star, accidentally live in one house.

name: After the Storm
summary: A surprising exit is followed by a glamorous new arrival to the group.

show.name: Written in the Stars
show.summary: In a stellar social experiment, singles representing each of the 12 zodiac signs are paired up by world-renowned astrologers. Matched using their birth charts, these new couples will find out if true love really is written in the stars.

show.name: 2PM Campus
show.summary: Our story made by women in their 20s, talking about lively topics that women in their 20s can worry about.

show.name: Мастер-классы Алексея Земскова
show.summary: Here you can find useful repair tips: how to save money, how to avoid mistakes, how to check workers, how to choose materials, how to design or do repair it yourself.

name: Two Points
summary: Joe seeks assistance from Christo, a shady individual, to help make a life altering decision.

show.name: Dying for a Living
show.summary: When a ruthless assassin encounters the most difficult job of his life, his search for answers catapults him into a deadly game of cat and mouse. Will he be able to survive and find redemption, or will he succumb to the darkness that threatens to consume him?

name: Cookie Sykes Goes for a Fun Run

show.name: Cookie Sykes Goes
show.summary: After going on holiday to Scotland, UK, Cookie Sykes and her owner, Tom Sykes decided to start a web series of adventurous videos, visiting different places and locations in the local area of Hampshire, UK. Cookie Sykes Goes was created and premiered 26 August 2019 on Cookie Sykes' YouTube channel, managed by Pythona Studios.

show.name: Yan Zhi's Love Story
show.summary: Yan Ning is a girl who is not good at words. She has been in love with Shen Zhi Zhou for many years but can't face the ending of being rejected. She chooses to erase her feelings for Shen Zhi Zhou through psychotherapy; Shen Zhi Zhou is a man who does not believe in love, because he is afraid of losing his best friend. Avoid feeling for Yan Ning. Two public figures are fettered by each other again because of a star dating show. They work together and overcome many difficulties, and finally realize that running away is not the best option, and only facing them can bring happiness to each other.

show.name: Mermaze Mermaidz
show.summary: Beyond the waves, beneath the surf, and into the deep blue lies the gleaming underwater world of the Mermaze Mermaidz. Light and color have started disappearing from Mystic City, so best friends Kishiko, Shellnelle, Harmonique, Riviera, and Jordie are granted a magical color change power that they must use to save their home before the city loses its sparkle for good. Follow the fabulous fins of these mermaids, each a celebrity in their own field, as they learn to control their powers, work to save the city, and meet new friends along the way.

name: What Democrats Could Learn from Republicans with Brian Beutler
summary: This week, a Crooked Media crossover event as Brian Beutler, host of Positively Dreadful, sits down with Jon to talk all the things Democrats could learn from Republicans. Yep, you read that right. Brian makes the case that when it comes to messaging, Democrats should be less shy and spend more energy drawing attention to Republican scandals and controversies — just like the GOP did for Hillary's emails, the migrant caravan, or crime. He talks to Jon about the obstacles in front of the Democratic party, what will matter to swing voters in 2024, and how the Republican Party is already on the hunt for the next Benghazi.

show.name: Offline with Jon Favreau
show.summary: Offline with Jon Favreau is a different kind of Sunday show – a chance to step away from our Twitter-fueled news cycles to hear smarter, lighter conversations about all the ways that our extremely online existence is shaping everything from politics and culture to the ways we live, work, and interact with one another. Join Jon each week as he asks us to put down our screens, grab our headphones, and figure out how to live happier, healthier lives, both on and offline.

show.name: The Queen's Umbrella
show.summary: A drama that deals with the top 1% education method of princes in the Joseon Dynasty and depicts the struggle of China to make troublemaking princes of the royal family into real princes.

name: Episode 8
summary: On the day of Sung Joon's wedding, Chairman Jin announces that he will no longer follow the rule of primogeniture and pass the company down to whoever proves their competence. The siblings of the Jin family eye on each other's shares, while Do Joon eggs on the siblings to mistrust each other.

show.name: Reborn Rich
show.summary: After ten years, a loyal employee is framed for embezzlement, then murdered by his employers, only to be reborn as their youngest son, with a yearn for revenge guiding his hostile takeover.

show.name: Invert: Jozuka Hisui Toujoshu
show.summary:
Adapted from the novel "Invert: Jozuka Hisui Toujoshu" (invert 城塚翡翠 倒叙集) by Aizawa Sako (相沢沙呼). 

Invert: Jozuka Hisui Toujoshu is the sequel of previous work Reibai Tantei Jozuka Hisui. This is the first time in the renzoku drama history where the same main character is featured in two separate dramas with different titles and posters.

show.name: This Week in Tech
show.summary: Your first podcast of the week is the last word in tech. Join the top tech pundits in a roundtable discussion of the latest trends in high tech. Hosted by Leo Laporte and friends.

name: Flight of the Mayflowers
summary: One city's heartbreak is another city's dream as Peyton learns the real story behind the most notorious move in sports history - the Colts leaving Baltimore for Indianapolis. Peyton surprises die hard Baltimore Colts fans and then meets up with an old friend in Indianapolis to explore what really happened the night the Colts left town.

show.name: Peyton's Places
show.summary: Peyton's Places offers a fun, insightful tour through 100 years of football, following the sport and the league's rise to an American cultural touchstone. For nearly a year, Manning has crisscrossed the country, visiting the people and places that have played an important part in the making of the NFL—highlighting memorable events, teams, players, and trends over the past century.

name: More Than a Meal
summary: One of Erin's biggest dreams becomes reality: she opens a storefront.

show.name: The Lost Kitchen
show.summary: Erin French is the owner of The Lost Kitchen, a historic mill turned restaurant in Freedom, Maine, population 722. Every year, hundreds of visitors from around the world make reservations not by phone or email, but by submitting postcards.

name: Entrepreneur Week
summary: Makenna experiments with new classes for a group of entrepreneurs.

show.name: La Pitchoune: Cooking in France
show.summary: Makenna Held bought Julia Child's home in France and turned it into a recipe-free cooking school. Now, she and her team welcome students into this iconic kitchen where enthusiasts learn to step out of their comfort zone and tap into their intuition.

name: Overlanding Trailer
summary: Ian takes a tag-along trailer and adds what he needs to live off the grid.

show.name: Fourwheeler
show.summary: If it has wheels and goes off road, Ian Johnson will work on it. From upgrading daily drivers to building a custom tub-chassis rock crawler, he takes you along on a do-it-yourself ride that tackles any kind of job.

name: Spinach Soup and Arepas
summary: Make an easy and delicious comfort meal with this soup and sandwich spin.

show.name: Everyday Cooking
show.summary: Samantha Seneviratne reveals that even on your busiest days, every home cooked meal can still be easy, exciting and full of flavor.

name: Christmas
summary: Dodger attempts a kind-hearted deed for an old friend on Christmas Eve but has to break into 10 Downing Street. As he gets trapped there, the gang try to steal 200 geese.

show.name: Dodger
show.summary: Ducking and diving through the tough London streets, trying to keep one step ahead of the law – hold onto your top hats, Dodger and the gang are in for one heck of a ride!

name: Varjo menneisyydestä
summary: Luisa (Maria Romero) and Hilkka (Riitta Havukainen) receive a tip that leads to extensive searches. However, the tentacles seem to stretch in many directions, and no one is willing to talk. Relations between Finns on the Sunshine Coast are getting tighter. Luisa has to face an unpleasant person from her recent past who makes it difficult for her to work.

show.name: Paratiisi
show.summary: A Finnish family is found murdered in cold blood in Fuengirola on the Spanish Costa del Sol. A criminal investigator from Finland is sent to solve a homicide that shocked Fuengirola's Finnish community.

name: The 12th Annual Streamy Awards
summary: Will be held at The Beverly Hilton in Los Angeles and hosted by the Youtuber Eric Decker. With a performance by Yung Gravy.

show.name: The Streamy Awards
show.summary: The Streamy Awards honor the best in online video and the creators behind it. The annual event brings together the biggest names in YouTube and online video for a night of celebration, discovery, and meaningful recognition.

name: The Race Is On
summary: Up-and-coming singer Tammy Wynette gets a big break when she's asked to open for her idol, country legend George Jones. The two have an immediate romantic connection and undeniable musical chemistry, but their would-be pairing faces a major obstacle: Tammy's husband Don Chapel.

show.name: George & Tammy
show.summary: George & Tammy chronicles the country music power couple, Tammy Wynette and George Jones, whose complicated relationship inspired some of the most iconic music of all time.
